{
  "texts": [
    "In Figure 4, amazon_counterfactual_en and mtop_domain have a consistent evaluation bias across m for n = 500 and n = 200, respectively.",
    "But these tasks did not result in an evaluation bias in any other experiment configuration, including those with GPT-2 and Mistral 7B.",
    "Care has to be taken when attempting to analyze or interpret acc extraacc base and acc testacc extra together.",
    "That's because these differences are not independent: if acc extra is high, then acc extra acc base increases and acc testacc extra decreases.",
    "This paper does not analyze the scores together, per se."
  ]
}